data.description: Welcome home! This wonderful End unit townhome is ready for new owners and new memories! With 1569 Sq feet and a 2 Car garage. This home features three spacious bedrooms and two and a half baths all meticulously engineered to make the perfect use of space. You will love the open kitchen/dining concept, flowing into the living room. It also features a first-floor bedroom/office with a screened lanai. The second-floor features 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. And a spacious living area for family leisure. Upstairs living area can easily be converted to a 4th bedroom.
